channel.description:
Hi, welcome to my channel! I'm just another small youtuber/mapper, and I hope you will like my videos and subscribe! I work really hard on making my videos decent, and I hope you like them. I also like to respond to comments on my videos.

I rule Vordalkien, Caravor, The Melville Horde, Bargow, Tyberny, Akkér, Assarion, and Valgond. Oh, and Galloth too, but nobody likes Galloth. Right?

My opinion of tacos? Perfectly fine.

Thanks for 200,000 views and 1,200 subscribers! That's just..... wow. And I just KNOW that sometime in the future I will get 2,000 subscribers, and YOU can help me with that.

Here are some other cool mappers.
